s=m><span class=title> Mana Battery</span><hr size=1> Something kinda funny happened to me last night, I'm pretty sure it wasn't a scam, but it was awfully odd.<br>
<br>
I was chatting with another shaman at the FV bank and she was pretty excited about a new mana regen device a friend of hers had bought in Iceclad, a mana battery.  She claimed that it made her husband regen mana 3 times as fast, and offered to sell me one for 62 plat.<br>
<br>
I just want everybody to know, that class V mana batteries are used by tinkers to make watchman armor, I doubt seriously they provide any kind of mana regen.<br>
<br>
